OL,3,CPolice give update on investigation
OL,4,Cinto 'unprecedented' ice hockey death
OL,6,FDetectives say they have been "working
OL,7,Fmeticulously to fully understand the
OL,8,Funprecedented circumstances" of Adam
OL,9,FJohnson's death during an ice hockey
OL,10,Fmatch.
OL,12,FSouth Yorkshire Police issued an
OL,13,Fupdate as a man arrested on suspicion
OL,14,Fof manslaughter was bailed again -
OL,15,Fmore than a year after the incident.
OL,17,FJohnson, who was 29, was playing for
OL,18,FNottingham Panthers against Sheffield
OL,19,FSteelers when he was hit in the neck
OL,20,Fby an opposition player's skate on 28
OL,21,FOctober 2023.
