OL,3,CPolice give update on investigation
OL,4,Cinto 'unprecedented' ice hockey death
OL,6,FHe died in hospital. A post-mortem
OL,7,Fexamination confirmed his cause of
OL,8,Fdeath as a neck injury.
OL,10,FA man was arrested on suspicion of
OL,11,Fmanslaughter in November 2023 and
OL,12,Fgiven bail by South Yorkshire Police.
OL,14,FOn Monday, the force said he had been
OL,15,Frebailed until 20 January next year.
OL,17,FDet Ch Insp Benjamin Wood said: "We
OL,18,Fhave been working meticulously to
OL,19,Ffully understand the unprecedented
OL,20,Fcircumstances in which Adam sadly lost
OL,21,Fhis life.
