OL,3,CPolice give update on investigation
OL,4,Cinto 'unprecedented' ice hockey death
OL,6,FIn January, Sheffield's senior
OL,7,Fcoroner, Tanyka Rawden, suspended her
OL,8,Finvestigation while the police inquiry
OL,9,Ftook its course.
OL,11,FIt emerged later that Ms Rawden had
OL,12,Fissued a Prevention of Future Deaths
OL,13,FReport to Ice Hockey UK and the
OL,14,FEnglish Ice Hockey Association (EIHA)
OL,15,Fabout the use of neck guards in the
OL,16,Fsport.
